<p>The <code>exists</code> tag checks if a file exists.</p>

<h2>Check File Exists</h2>
<pre>{open}exists APP . 'fragments/claude/index.pad'{close}
  File exists
{open}else{close}
  File not found
{open}/exists{close}</pre>
{exists APP . 'fragments/claude/index.pad'}
<p style="color:green">File exists: fragments/claude/index.pad</p>
{else}
<p style="color:red">File not found</p>
{/exists}

<h2>Check Non-Existent File</h2>
<pre>{open}exists APP . 'fragments/claude/nonexistent.pad'{close}
  Found
{open}else{close}
  Not found
{open}/exists{close}</pre>
{exists APP . 'fragments/claude/nonexistent.pad'}
<p>Found</p>
{else}
<p style="color:red">Not found: fragments/claude/nonexistent.pad</p>
{/exists}

<h2>Note</h2>
<p>The exists tag uses APP constant for application-relative paths.</p>
